            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Mercurio <lb n="2"/>Augusto <expan><abbr>sacr</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> &amp;lt;C=G&amp;gt;iltius Celtil<lb break="no" n="4"/>li <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> Quirina Cos<lb break="no" n="5"/>sus IIIIIIvir <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustalis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>oco</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ato</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ecreto</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ecurionum</ex></expan> 
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Wohl der Mittelteil einer Statuenbasis. Bei der Auffindung waren Reste von roter Farbe in den Buchstaben erhalten. Höhe, Breite, Tiefe nach lupa 8445. Hedera in Z. 3. (B): Walser: Z. 3: Ciltius.</p>
            </div>
